<img class="post_image aligncenter" src="http://www.runtogold.com/images/goldmoney-scam-fraud.jpg" width="520" height="79" alt="goldmoney.com scam, goldmoney scam, goldmoney.com fraud, goldmoney fraud, problems, compaints" />
					<h1>No Evidence Of GoldMoney.com Scam Fraud Complaints Or Problems</h1>
					<p class="headline_meta"><span><a href="http://www.runtogold.com/goldmoney/goldmoney-scam-goldmoney-fraud-complaints-problems/#comments" rel="nofollow">5 comments</a></span></p>
				</div>
				<div class="format_text">
            <a href="http://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" 
